Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.80,0:00:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請保持室內光亮，別太近看唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.53,0:00:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.40,0:02:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點，快點，我們二個先去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.31,0:02:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡鈴加小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.57,0:02:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小卡鈴加，你想對主人做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.71,0:02:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是和他牽手而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.35,0:02:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久美姊姊也和沙希姊姊牽手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.22,0:02:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這主意不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.88,0:02:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人是屬於久留美我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.29,0:02:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是我的仲人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.92,0:02:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你又來了...呀，又開始吵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.34,0:02:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之我們來出雲的目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.77,0:03:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是為了找出綾小路博士的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.74,0:03:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秘密研究所的地點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.24,0:03:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後找出拐走博士的敵人的行蹤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.35,0:03:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你們不要做無謂的吵架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.18,0:03:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.28,0:03:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.95,0:03:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼!啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.39,0:03:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美 卡鈴加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.46,0:03:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們二個別吵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.16,0:03:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要，是小卡鈴加的錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.73,0:03:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我並沒有錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.63,0:03:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這並不是哪邊的錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.46,0:03:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是我們必須好好聽博士的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.60,0:03:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.17,0:03:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人的話是絕對的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.97,0:03:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.14,0:03:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.01,0:03:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以問問在後山瀑布下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.34,0:03:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,修練的那些道者，也許智有發現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.70,0:03:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,情況如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.37,0:03:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們說沒看過類似那樣的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.70,0:04:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們這麼辛苦來到出雲...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.11,0:04:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再去別的地方問問看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.42,0:04:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.62,0:04:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連湯都這麼棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.79,0:04:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的，好好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.73,0:04:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好飽，剩下的給仲人吃 啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.24,0:04:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,張口   啊~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.44,0:04:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，身為姊姊，你怎麼可以這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.74,0:04:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.65,0:04:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們二個不要再吵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.28,0:04:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我感覺到了     嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.05,0:04:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.13,0:05:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們是久留美，沙希和卡鈴加吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.00,0:05:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.87,0:05:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾小路博士不在這裡嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.51,0:05:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你...為何知道綾小路博士這個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.62,0:05:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被帶走了...是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.42,0:05:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來和博士預料的一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.88,0:05:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.59,0:06:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問...你到底是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.84,0:06:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.17,0:06:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是綾小路博士第一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.08,0:06:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,踏上這個土地的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.68,0:06:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己親自動手完成的研究室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.75,0:06:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，那不是久留美的照片嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.25,0:06:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為何會出現在這裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.52,0:06:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實大家原本應該在這裡甦醒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.36,0:06:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.63,0:06:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後由古早以前就製造完成的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.60,0:06:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來守護這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.27,0:06:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，那麼你也是鋼鐵天使嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.84,0:06:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，忘記向你們介紹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.01,0:06:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫做撫子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.28,0:06:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽從博士的命令，一直守著這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.72,0:07:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才說「和博士預料的一樣」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.49,0:07:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.26,0:07:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想抓走博士的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.13,0:07:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是"ACADEMY"的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.13,0:07:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"ACADEMY"?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.86,0:07:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是製造我們的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.53,0:07:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊~原來那裡叫ACADEMY
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.40,0:07:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"ACADEMY"是什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.80,0:07:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了改寫人類的歷史
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.24,0:07:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而從未來來的一群科學家集團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.44,0:07:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾小路博士也是其中一人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.15,0:07:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從未來...你是說博士是未來人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.99,0:07:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾小路博士與其他人對立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.96,0:07:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後逃出了研究所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.99,0:07:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們對於ANGELHEART
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.76,0:07:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的想法是錯誤的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.16,0:07:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博士每次都是這樣講
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.37,0:07:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾小路博到底想做什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.14,0:07:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想利用久留美她們來作什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.21,0:08:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博士是為了將自己開發的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.34,0:08:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ANGELHEART. 改
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.91,0:08:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用這個力量來保護全人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.28,0:08:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，是為了保護全世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.95,0:08:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了達成這個目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.66,0:08:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,需要技術熟練的法師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.76,0:08:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就是博士所尋找的人吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.60,0:08:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.67,0:08:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擁有改的只有你一個吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.17,0:08:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另外一個在那裡呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.04,0:08:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想應該是被那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.78,0:08:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「ACADEMY」給搶走了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.58,0:08:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.08,0:08:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人，久留美完全聽不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.99,0:08:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界的命運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.82,0:08:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全部都操縱在ANGEL
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.92,0:08:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,HEART，改的手中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.39,0:08:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後收有ANGEL
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.09,0:08:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,HEART 改的鋼鐵天使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.43,0:08:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由擁有正義的能者所控制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.14,0:09:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在笑什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.47,0:09:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我太高興了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.74,0:09:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人對久留美的愛可以拯救世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.21,0:09:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是為了這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.65,0:09:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不只這樣，愛的力量是很大的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.02,0:09:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很可惜，仲人的愛已經屬於我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.52,0:09:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.82,0:09:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有，因為我們在火車上親吻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.13,0:09:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘴對嘴的     你騙人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.60,0:09:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然你去問本人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.47,0:09:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然說為了保護世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.11,0:09:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以需要我的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.61,0:09:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我知卻什麼也沒做到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.72,0:09:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.52,0:09:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.82,0:09:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人，和卡鈴加KISS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.06,0:09:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.42,0:09:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，那是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.16,0:09:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是真的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.63,0:10:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，那只是巧合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.60,0:10:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美只有主人一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.73,0:10:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是主人卻不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.03,0:10:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.31,0:10:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人，久留美和卡鈴加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.24,0:10:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你比較喜歡那個?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.35,0:10:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊...   那個?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.68,0:10:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你問我那個...我和卡鈴加剛認識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.55,0:10:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼只問久留美一個     啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.49,0:10:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡久留美嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.13,0:10:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不太清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.53,0:10:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是只要和久留美小姐一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.27,0:10:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就感到很快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.30,0:10:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜歡主人唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.34,0:10:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.01,0:10:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.41,0:10:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美...現在我先想靜一靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.65,0:10:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有些事情我想好好的想一想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.32,0:12:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.52,0:12:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仲人...請救救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.39,0:12:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請助我一臂之力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.09,0:12:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要你的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.87,0:12:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.35,0:12:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.28,0:12:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「到達出雲了!」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.51,0:14:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人，你怎麼可以丟下久留美呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.68,0:14:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.05,0:14:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,次回 鋼鐵天使久留美第18話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.32,0:14:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是真的    撒謊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.79,0:14:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們再也見不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.86,0:14:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是真的   主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.49,0:14:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人     主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.60,0:14:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丟下久留美到哪裡去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.63,0:14:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.53,0:14:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然沒有回應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.90,0:14:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?以前不都是這樣預告嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.84,0:14:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的，這次好像不太一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.48,0:14:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那仲人真的不會回來了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.68,0:14:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,次回 鋼鐵天使久留美第18話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.48,0:14:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「那是騙人的!」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.95,0:14:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對，不可能的    主人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.06,0:15:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請保持室內光亮，別太近看唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.30,0:15:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰?
